32
00:08:37,617 --> 00:08:39,608
He's woken up?

33
00:08:45,558 --> 00:08:51,190
How many years has he been silent?

34
00:08:51,898 --> 00:08:54,423
I'm an old man now...

35
00:08:54,800 --> 00:08:58,170
so obsessed with a sap that doesn't exist...

36
00:08:58,205 --> 00:09:00,434
I've lost track of time.

37
00:09:06,078 --> 00:09:08,205
A niger triggerfish!

38
00:09:12,885 --> 00:09:15,183
He's after it again!

39
00:09:32,038 --> 00:09:35,872
Baron! There's going to be lightning!

40
00:10:56,255 --> 00:10:58,189
No, Xian!

41
00:10:58,491 --> 00:11:00,324
That's not crosskahla!

42
00:11:00,359 --> 00:11:02,793
It's a stone! It's just a stone!

43
00:11:03,062 --> 00:11:04,620
Snap out of it, Xian!

44
00:11:04,797 --> 00:11:06,196
Xian!

45
00:11:19,612 --> 00:11:22,672
No, Palme!

46
00:11:45,838 --> 00:11:48,534
