171
00:27:50,902 --> 00:27:52,369
Did you hear me?

172
00:28:14,292 --> 00:28:18,763
Forget that! Go home and
you'll get sold off again.

173
00:28:18,798 --> 00:28:21,163
Parents are worthless.

174
00:28:23,034 --> 00:28:26,787
We're going to knock over the Boss of this town

175
00:28:26,822 --> 00:28:30,541
