01:24:04,406 --> 01:24:09,469
It's only a guess, but perhaps the
memory is repeating itself.

796
01:24:10,345 --> 01:24:17,152
Or perhaps Soma intends to negate the
world he created, including us...

797
01:24:17,187 --> 01:24:20,088
and give it to Laala.

798
01:24:20,123 --> 01:24:21,555
"Negate?!"

799
01:24:25,026 --> 01:24:30,293
We shall prevent the birth of Laala and
break away from Soma!

800
01:24:31,032 --> 01:24:34,399
We of Tamas shall take control of our destiny!

801
01:25:20,081 --> 01:25:21,548
Father...

802
01:25:49,043 --> 01:25:50,840
Popo!

803
01:25:51,179 --> 01:25:53,647
Where are you?

804
01:26:01,956 --> 01:26:03,184
A bola...

805
01:26:06,227 --> 01:26:09,685
Did you show me a dream of my father?

806
01:26:17,005 --> 01:26:17,670
Come here...

807
01:26:17,705 --> 01:26:18,506
Here she is!
Come here...

808
01:26:18,541 --> 01:26:19,139
Here she is!

809
01:26:19,174 --> 01:26:21,904
Palme! I found Popo! Palme!

810
01:26:22,310 --> 01:26:24,612
We've been looking all over for you!

811
01:26:24,647 --> 01:26:26,047
What were you doing?!

812
01:26:26,082 --> 01:26:26,103
Popo!

813
01:26:37,692 --> 01:26:40,286
You shouldn't be wandering around like that!

814
01:26:45,066 --> 01:26:47,694
Palme?

815
01:26:47,936 --> 01:26:49,665
A bola!

816
01:26:51,873 --> 01:26:52,705
I'll get rid of it!

817
01:26:52,740 --> 01:26:53,374
No!
I'll get rid of it!

818
01:26:53,409 --> 01:26:54,207
No!

819
01:26:54,242 --> 01:26:56,369
This one's gentle...

820
01:26:57,145 --> 01:26:58,612
Popo!

821
01:27:00,415 --> 01:27:03,213
You! Get out of here!

822
01:27:03,551 --> 01:27:05,118
Stay away from her!

823
01:27:05,153 --> 01:27:07,280
No, Palme! The poor thing!

824
01:27:15,430 --> 01:27:18,365
I was worried about you!

825
01:27:20,835 --> 01:27:22,427
Popo, you're acting strange!

826
01:27:24,205 --> 01:27:26,736
Things like this start hanging around

827
01:27:26,771 --> 01:27:29,268
because you never cheer up and act human.

828
01:27:29,811 --> 01:27:32,871
At this rate I'll never become human!

829
01:27:33,381 --> 01:27:35,212
I... I...

830
01:27:41,856 --> 01:27:43,084
Shatta...

831
01:27:44,659 --> 01:27:46,991
Palme... that's enough.

832
01:27:50,298 --> 01:27:51,765
Come on, Palme.

833
01:28:05,747 --> 01:28:07,214
Popo...

834
01:29:05,640 --> 01:29:08,443
Look! That's the Stone Pillar of Toto, right?

835
01:29:08,478 --> 01:29:11,139
Yep. We're almost there.

836
01:29:16,417 --> 01:29:17,216
An aguri!

837
01:29:17,251 --> 01:29:17,919
It's just a baby! What's wrong?
An aguri!

838
01:29:17,954 --> 01:29:19,654
It's just a baby! What's wrong?

839
01:29:19,689 --> 01:29:21,144
It's shaking!

840
01:29:28,863 --> 01:29:30,091
Take cover!

841
01:29:41,109 --> 01:29:42,576
Shatta!

842
01:30:59,086 --> 01:31:00,644
Wow!

843
01:31:04,992 --> 01:31:06,653
You're the aguri from earlier today!

844
01:31:10,364 --> 01:31:11,956
Come here...

845
01:31:14,869 --> 01:31:17,235
Come on! That's it.

846
01:31:19,907 --> 01:31:21,738
Nice aguri...

847
01:31:56,811 --> 01:31:58,511
That's awful!

848
01:31:58,546 --> 01:32:00,681
And after we went to the trouble of saving it!

849
01:32:00,716 --> 01:32:02,911
Palme, did you do this?

850
01:32:03,918 --> 01:32:04,617
No!

851
01:32:04,652 --> 01:32:05,386
Then who did?
No!

852
01:32:05,421 --> 01:32:06,252
Then who did?

853
01:32:06,287 --> 01:32:07,854
Who else could have?

854
01:32:07,889 --> 01:32:12,588
I... I don't know anything about it! I don't! I don't!

855
01:32:30,645 --> 01:32:33,478
How long are you going to stay
like that? Enough already!

856
01:32:34,482 --> 01:32:39,078
Do something, Palme! She's
been like this all day!

857
01:32:46,060 --> 01:32:47,960
It's time to go.

858
01:32:54,101 --> 01:32:56,501
Do you want to turn to stone?

859
01:32:57,572 --> 01:32:59,563
I want to become human.

860
01:33:01,175 --> 01:33:03,166
Aren't you sad?

861
01:33:04,245 --> 01:33:05,735
I'm a puppet.

862
01:33:06,380 --> 01:33:10,516
You didn't used to be like that!
You're strange now!

863
01:33:10,551 --> 01:33:13,281
I know I'm strange! That's why I'm
trying to become human.

864
01:33:15,089 --> 01:33:16,556
Palme...

865
01:33:26,734 --> 01:33:28,201
What's this?!

866
01:33:44,051 --> 01:33:45,518
Hurry.

867
01:33:46,921 --> 01:33:48,388
Hurry.

868
01:33:50,391 --> 01:33:52,222
Soma awaits.

869
01:33:53,561 --> 01:33:55,028
Hurry.

870
01:33:56,063 --> 01:33:57,963
Soma is waiting for you.

871
01:34:03,004 --> 01:34:04,883
For... for me?

872
01:34:04,918 --> 01:34:06,762
Soma is waiting.

873
01:34:07,975 --> 01:34:10,042
Soma's waiting for me?

874
01:34:10,077 --> 01:34:12,238
Soma is waiting for you to come.

875
01:34:14,315 --> 01:34:15,782
Hurry.

876
01:34:18,085 --> 01:34:19,151
It's gone!

877
01:34:19,186 --> 01:34:19,587
What was that? A ghost?
It's gone!

878
01:34:19,622 --> 01:34:21,851
What was that? A ghost?

879
01:34:25,292 --> 01:34:27,760
Soma's waiting for me!

880
01:34:34,769 --> 01:34:37,897
Hurry, Popo! Quick!

881
01:34:40,274 --> 01:34:43,266
Palme! Take it easy!

882
01:34:46,447 --> 01:34:47,914
Palme...

883
01:34:49,083 --> 01:34:50,778
What, Shatta?

884
01:34:51,352 --> 01:34:53,183
Are you OK, Popo?

885
01:34:55,756 --> 01:34:57,951
Show me that capsule.

886
01:34:59,994 --> 01:35:02,588
Something about it bothers me.

887
01:35:09,603 --> 01:35:11,539
You want to steal it!

888
01:35:11,574 --> 01:35:13,105
Huh? Palme...

889
01:35:13,140 --> 01:35:17,489
I knew it! You're from Below, just like those men!

890
01:35:17,524 --> 01:35:21,839
What are you talking about?
Shatta wouldn't do that!

891
01:35:22,249 --> 01:35:24,817
This is the most important thing I have!

892
01:35:24,852 --> 01:35:28,219
I won't let anyone touch it! Not even Shatta!

893
01:35:29,857 --> 01:35:31,324
Suit yourself.

894
01:35:34,295 --> 01:35:36,763
I don't need this thing from Below.

895
01:35:38,499 --> 01:35:43,003
I'll... I'll be fine without you, Shatta!

896
01:35:43,038 --> 01:35:45,372
Soma will protect me!

897
01:35:45,407 --> 01:35:46,941
Come on, Popo!

898
01:35:46,976 --> 01:35:48,408
Palme!

899
01:35:48,709 --> 01:35:53,408
You talk big for a puppet! There's no
way you'll ever become human!

900
01:35:54,648 --> 01:35:56,115
Shatta!

901
01:36:24,845 --> 01:36:26,642
Popo! We're almost there!

902
01:36:29,517 --> 01:36:32,509
I'll become a human! A human!

903
01:36:33,220 --> 01:36:34,789
It won't be long now!

904
01:36:34,824 --> 01:36:37,223
Soon! Soon!

905
01:36:39,293 --> 01:36:43,093
Soon... Soon I'll be with my father...

906
01:36:57,444 --> 01:36:59,810
We leave tomorrow, without the girl.

907
01:37:00,247 --> 01:37:02,448
Gandel, what are you saying?

908
01:37:02,483 --> 01:37:04,576
Do you intend to leave Koram to die?

909
01:37:05,019 --> 01:37:07,852
The future of Tamas is in our hands.

910
01:37:08,189 --> 01:37:11,125
I won't allow any more setbacks.

911
01:37:11,160 --> 01:37:12,524
She'll die!

912
01:37:14,228 --> 01:37:17,220
I don't care. I have sons.

913
01:37:18,766 --> 01:37:20,233
Father...

914
01:37:23,871 --> 01:37:25,771
I'm better now.

915
01:37:27,675 --> 01:37:29,302
I'm all better!

916
01:37:58,839 --> 01:38:01,108
We're almost there, Popo. We've got to go down.

917
01:38:01,143 --> 01:38:02,541
No, Palme.

918
01:38:04,578 --> 01:38:06,312
I can't!

919
01:38:06,347 --> 01:38:09,282
What are you saying? After we've come this far?

920
01:38:10,017 --> 01:38:12,383
All we have to do is go down there! C'mon!

921
01:38:16,056 --> 01:38:17,590
Popo! We're going down! Now!

922
01:38:17,625 --> 01:38:18,025
Ow!
Popo! We're going down! Now!

923
01:38:18,060 --> 01:38:18,791
Ow!

924
01:38:18,826 --> 01:38:19,126
Ow!
Soon I'll be human! Don't give
me any more trouble!

925
01:38:19,161 --> 01:38:23,230
Soon I'll be human! Don't give
me any more trouble!

926
01:38:23,265 --> 01:38:25,221
Think more about MY predicament!

927
01:38:26,967 --> 01:38:28,832
Popo! What's the matter?!

928
01:38:29,470 --> 01:38:30,937
P-Popo!

929
01:38:31,472 --> 01:38:34,675
Wh-what's wrong? What is it? C'mon, get up!

930
01:38:34,710 --> 01:38:36,506
Popo! Popo!

931
01:38:37,044 --> 01:38:40,036
What do I do? What do I do?
What am I going to do?

932
01:38:44,752 --> 01:38:46,219
Damn these things!

933
01:38:50,658 --> 01:38:52,558
Tamas is down there.

934
01:38:53,227 --> 01:38:55,029
It's pitch-black!

935
01:38:55,064 --> 01:38:56,496
Look!

936
01:39:03,103 --> 01:39:07,938
Soon I'll be human, then I can
be with Popo forever!

937
01:39:17,851 --> 01:39:19,944
Father! Father!

938
01:39:20,821 --> 01:39:22,083
Father!

939
01:39:23,490 --> 01:39:25,685
I warned you about the storm!

940
01:39:25,926 --> 01:39:27,985
Gandel! Hang in there!

941
01:39:29,663 --> 01:39:32,466
It's no use. His foot's caught in the roots!

942
01:39:32,501 --> 01:39:33,832
Someone get down there!

943
01:39:33,867 --> 01:39:34,268
I'll do it!
Someone get down there!

944
01:39:34,303 --> 01:39:35,000
I'll do it!

945
01:39:35,035 --> 01:39:35,369
I'll do it!
Koram!

946
01:39:35,404 --> 01:39:36,495
Koram!

947
01:39:38,305 --> 01:39:41,706
Just a little bit more, Father! Just a little bit!

948
01:39:46,580 --> 01:39:47,546
OK! He's free!

949
01:39:47,581 --> 01:39:48,082
Now! Heave!
OK! He's free!

950
01:39:48,117 --> 01:39:49,048
Now! Heave!

951
01:39:49,083 --> 01:39:49,249
Now! Heave!
Heave!

952
01:39:49,284 --> 01:39:50,341
Heave!

953
01:39:56,056 --> 01:39:57,614
Well done, Koram!

954
01:39:59,226 --> 01:40:00,955
Father! Are you all right?

955
01:40:04,031 --> 01:40:05,498
Gandel!

956
01:40:10,738 --> 01:40:12,205
Father!

957
01:40:12,973 --> 01:40:16,136
How could I have been so careless?

958
01:40:24,985 --> 01:40:26,452
Father...

959
01:40:27,154 --> 01:40:28,621
Father...

960
01:40:46,273 --> 01:40:47,740
That smells nice...

961
01:40:57,951 --> 01:41:02,081
I like you just the way you are, Palme.
The way you are right now.

962
01:41:03,924 --> 01:41:05,391
Can you walk?

963
01:41:06,160 --> 01:41:07,659
Palme! Your arm!

964
01:41:07,694 --> 01:41:10,925
It's nothing. I just got too much sun on it.

965
01:41:21,008 --> 01:41:22,600
Popo!

966
01:41:26,380 --> 01:41:27,847
Palme!

967
01:41:39,359 --> 01:41:40,826
Baron!

968
01:41:53,307 --> 01:41:56,577
It's definitely there! It's reacting
to a very strong will!

969
01:41:56,612 --> 01:41:58,909
Quick, before Soma notices!

970
01:42:05,752 --> 01:42:09,523
Don't take the Egg! Please! Stop!

971
01:42:09,558 --> 01:42:11,991
I need it to become human!

972
01:42:12,426 --> 01:42:18,387
Popo, help! Where are you, Popo?!

973
01:42:20,701 --> 01:42:23,864
It's all right. We're just taking out the capsule.

974
01:42:26,273 --> 01:42:27,740
Palme...

975
01:42:29,243 --> 01:42:33,179
I heard that my mother left Tamas
when she was a baby.

976
01:42:34,081 --> 01:42:37,651
We've risked our lives to bring that capsule here!

977
01:42:37,686 --> 01:42:41,755
I'm amazed you brought the Egg of Touto.

978
01:42:41,790 --> 01:42:45,824
How ironic for the brave warriors of Sol!

979
01:42:46,560 --> 01:42:48,027
Watch your mouth!

980
01:42:49,329 --> 01:42:50,796
What's that?!

981
01:42:53,534 --> 01:42:55,714
What's that noise? Is it Soma?!

982
01:42:55,749 --> 01:42:57,895
Captain! It's coming from the lab!

983
01:43:13,220 --> 01:43:14,687
Popo!

984
01:43:15,856 --> 01:43:17,323
Palme!

985
01:43:22,930 --> 01:43:25,264
Was it that puppet?!

986
01:43:25,299 --> 01:43:29,235
What about the capsule?
Didn't you get it? Find it!

987
01:43:29,536 --> 01:43:31,766
He's going to see Soma!

988
01:43:46,486 --> 01:43:47,953
Palme?

989
01:43:54,027 --> 01:43:55,619
Shatta!

990
01:43:55,996 --> 01:43:58,260
Did you do this?

991
01:43:59,299 --> 01:44:01,833
Help me!

992
01:44:01,868 --> 01:44:03,529
Answer me! Palme!

993
01:44:16,917 --> 01:44:20,683
Father! Where are you?!

994
01:44:24,625 --> 01:44:26,092
Mother!

995
01:44:27,461 --> 01:44:29,053
What's happened?!

996
01:44:30,764 --> 01:44:32,231
It can't be!

997
01:44:33,400 --> 01:44:34,867
Palme!

998
01:44:42,709 --> 01:44:44,176
Popo...

999
01:44:45,846 --> 01:44:49,942
Let's go see Soma.

1000
01:44:55,889 --> 01:44:57,481
Popo!

1001
01:44:58,525 --> 01:45:00,390
No! No!

1002
01:45:01,161 --> 01:45:02,822
Stop, Palme!

1003
01:45:04,531 --> 01:45:08,331
I'm sorry, but I can't let you go see Soma.

1004
01:45:10,270 --> 01:45:15,731
Besides, what's inside that capsule
you've got isn't the soul of Touto!

1005
01:45:16,476 --> 01:45:19,179
Soma won't take it.

1006
01:45:19,214 --> 01:45:20,612
Palme!

1007
01:45:22,049 --> 01:45:26,645
You're lying! Soma said he was waiting for me!

1008
01:45:26,753 --> 01:45:31,781
Listen, Palme... it's my mother
who's in that capsule.

1009
01:45:31,958 --> 01:45:33,926
The spirit of my dead mother!

1010
01:45:41,468 --> 01:45:43,095
Stop it, Shatta!

1011
01:45:43,904 --> 01:45:47,974
Look! I've got the capsule!

1012
01:45:48,009 --> 01:45:50,008
So I'm going!

1013
01:45:50,043 --> 01:45:53,240
I'm sick and tired of being a stupid puppet!

1014
01:45:53,275 --> 01:45:56,438
I'm going to become a strong man like you!

1015
01:45:57,184 --> 01:45:59,744
I'm going to become human for Popo's sake.

1016
01:46:00,020 --> 01:46:03,114
I want to stay by her side forever!

1017
01:46:06,059 --> 01:46:09,586
Please! Let me become human!

1018
01:46:11,098 --> 01:46:12,565
Palme!

1019
01:46:14,968 --> 01:46:16,435
No, Palme.

1020
01:46:16,970 --> 01:46:21,839
My mother's spirit is crazy.
You can't give that to Soma.

1021
01:46:24,411 --> 01:46:27,346
Come on, Palme, let's go...

1022
01:46:27,714 --> 01:46:29,511
let's go to see Soma.

1023
01:46:30,217 --> 01:46:31,683
Popo!

1024
01:46:31,718 --> 01:46:35,956
What... what are you thinking?! Don't be a fool!

1025
01:46:35,991 --> 01:46:38,256
You're a human! Think!

1026
01:46:38,291 --> 01:46:41,522
You've heard what's happening in Tamas!

1027
01:46:42,229 --> 01:46:44,720
We can't let Laala be born!

1028
01:46:45,432 --> 01:46:48,128
Stop or I'll cut you down!

1029
01:46:50,637 --> 01:46:54,368
Don't you care what happens
here Below?! People will die!

1030
01:46:56,376 --> 01:46:59,641
Don't listen to that... that damn puppet!

1031
01:47:00,414 --> 01:47:03,144
Palme isn't a puppet.

1032
01:47:06,753 --> 01:47:09,244
You... you!

1033
01:47:26,106 --> 01:47:27,573
Look!

1034
01:47:43,056 --> 01:47:45,752
Quick! Soma's mobilizing!

1035
01:47:46,193 --> 01:47:49,424
When you find that puppet, destroy it
along with the capsule!

1036
01:48:27,033 --> 01:48:28,500
Palme!

1037
01:48:28,535 --> 01:48:30,196
Popo, we've got to hurry!

1038
01:48:42,983 --> 01:48:45,213
Father, where are you?!

1039
01:48:46,253 --> 01:48:51,623
I did... what my brothers couldn't.

1040
01:48:52,125 --> 01:48:54,320
I did it!

1041
01:48:55,462 --> 01:48:56,929
Father!

1042
01:48:57,597 --> 01:48:59,064
Father!

1043
01:49:02,435 --> 01:49:03,936
Popo!

1044
01:49:03,971 --> 01:49:05,437
Palme!

1045
01:49:21,588 --> 01:49:23,488
My body!

1046
01:49:37,470 --> 01:49:38,903
Soma!

1047
01:49:54,654 --> 01:49:56,121
Run!

1048
01:50:06,700 --> 01:50:08,065
Damn!

1049
01:50:08,301 --> 01:50:13,034
It's as though we're living inside of
Soma! There's no way we can win!

1050
01:50:16,943 --> 01:50:19,503
Popo! Popo!

1051
01:50:21,748 --> 01:50:24,182
Palme! Hang in there!

1052
01:50:28,288 --> 01:50:29,755
Fight it, Palme!

1053
01:50:37,831 --> 01:50:41,062
I want... to be human...

1054
01:50:47,040 --> 01:50:48,871
Popo!

1055
01:50:50,877 --> 01:50:53,880
Come on, Palme! Keep fighting!
Just a little more!

1056
01:50:53,915 --> 01:50:55,541
It's not much farther!

1057
01:51:09,029 --> 01:51:10,496
Palme!

1058
01:51:10,997 --> 01:51:12,828
Please! Stand up!

1059
01:51:17,203 --> 01:51:21,105
Soma's waiting! You're going to become human!

1060
01:51:25,645 --> 01:51:28,515
No! Don't turn into a tree!

1061
01:51:28,550 --> 01:51:29,982
No! No!

1062
01:51:30,350 --> 01:51:31,850
No!

1063
01:51:31,885 --> 01:51:36,256
You said you'd become a human
for me, Palme! Come on!

1064
01:51:36,291 --> 01:51:37,951
Palme!

1065
01:51:38,925 --> 01:51:40,392
