1073
01:52:29,609 --> 01:52:32,578
I'll go the rest of the way myself.

1074
01:52:36,216 --> 01:52:37,615
It's okay.

1075
01:52:38,251 --> 01:52:42,551
This is my punishment. It was
me who killed that baby aguri.

1076
01:52:44,190 --> 01:52:47,318
I can't stay with you.

1077
01:52:47,961 --> 01:52:52,921
No! I'll follow you wherever you go!
I'll stay with you always!

1078
01:53:10,049 --> 01:53:12,347
Answer me, Soma!

1079
01:53:12,986 --> 01:53:16,922
Show me my father! Don't hide him from me!

1080
01:53:24,864 --> 01:53:26,422
The blast! It stopped?!

1081
01:53:27,100 --> 01:53:28,567
Palme!

1082
01:53:37,710 --> 01:53:39,075
It's Palme!

1083
01:54:03,236 --> 01:54:05,932
Is that what was in the capsule?!

1084
01:54:12,178 --> 01:54:15,147
