Stop!
Popo, you'll die!

1099
01:55:42,904 --> 01:55:44,029
Popo, you'll die!

1100
01:55:44,570 --> 01:55:47,334
Please! Take me to the top of Palme!

1101
01:55:55,448 --> 01:55:57,848
It's going into Soma's forest!

1102
01:56:20,073 --> 01:56:22,064
Palme! Can you hear me?

1103
01:56:23,276 --> 01:56:24,743
Palme!

1104
01:56:30,516 --> 01:56:33,349
Please! Answer me!

1105
01:56:55,208 --> 01:56:57,176
