1106
01:56:58,644 --> 01:57:02,705
This place is just so quiet.

1107
01:57:10,923 --> 01:57:13,915
Someone's crying...

1108
01:57:17,797 --> 01:57:21,665
Who could it be?

1109
01:57:32,779 --> 01:57:34,246
A lute...

1110
01:57:35,148 --> 01:57:38,584
Palme, can you hear me?! Answer me!

1111
01:57:39,385 --> 01:57:43,890
You said we'd go to Xian's hometown! Together!

1112
01:57:43,925 --> 01:57:45,357
Please!

1113
01:57:47,060 --> 01:57:49,858
Come back, Palme!

1114
01:57:55,568 --> 01:57:56,830
I love you...

1115
01:58:11,884 --> 01:58:14,011
You don't have to do anything.

1116
01:58:15,188 --> 01:58:16,780
Just be with me.

1117
01:58:18,991 --> 01:58:20,720
Just stay here.

1118
01:58:21,994 --> 01:58:23,461
Palme...

1119
01:58:24,764 --> 01:58:26,231
Popo!

1120
01:58:52,558 --> 01:58:55,186
