02:01:09,762 --> 02:01:11,229
Grab on!

1134
02:01:12,665 --> 02:01:14,832
Palme! Help her!

1135
02:01:14,867 --> 02:01:17,301
Help Shatta's mother!

1136
02:01:18,938 --> 02:01:23,204
I know how it feels... because I wanted
my mother to hold me too.

1137
02:01:23,476 --> 02:01:24,943
Popo!

1138
02:01:34,754 --> 02:01:37,780
It was you crying, Koram...

1139
02:01:39,158 --> 02:01:42,491
You're the one who saved me.

