Laala!

1160
02:05:24,650 --> 02:05:26,117
Palme!

1161
02:05:51,210 --> 02:05:51,976
It's Palme!

1162
02:05:52,011 --> 02:05:52,711
Palme!
It's Palme!

1163
02:05:52,746 --> 02:05:53,377
Palme!

1164
02:05:53,412 --> 02:05:55,710
Look! He's still got the capsule!

1165
02:06:01,987 --> 02:06:04,114
It's heading for Laala! It's going inside her!

1166
02:06:12,831 --> 02:06:14,298
Palme?

1167
02:06:33,786 --> 02:06:35,481
The negation! It's started!

1168
02:06:58,611 --> 02:07:01,580
The destruction's stopped!

1169
02:07:10,689 --> 02:07:12,156
Shatta...

1170
02:07:12,958 --> 02:07:15,722
I know you're there, Shatta.

1171
02:07:16,795 --> 02:07:18,262
Mother?

1172
02:07:19,131 --> 02:07:20,598
Forgive me.

1173
02:07:21,967 --> 02:07:24,767
I never once held you...

1174
02:07:24,802 --> 02:07:27,567
Mother! Mother! Mother!!

1175
02:08:13,786 --> 02:08:14,652
Palme!

1176
02:08:14,687 --> 02:08:15,287
Popo!
Palme!

1177
02:08:15,322 --> 02:08:16,151
Popo!

1178
02:08:42,214 --> 02:08:43,681
Soma's dead!

1179
02:09:00,065 --> 02:09:02,499
Pools of crosskahla oil...

1180
02:09:05,437 --> 02:09:07,064
There's so much of it...

1181
