1210
02:12:10,022 --> 02:12:25,666
And walk without turning back

1211
02:12:46,725 --> 02:12:54,131
When you shed a tear

1212
02:12:57,069 --> 02:13:05,875
I'll bring you the scent of
honey you liked so much

1213
02:13:07,279 --> 02:13:15,118
It shined on your fingers

1214
02:13:37,576 --> 02:13:48,019
I'll be by your side, quietly

